{
  "stem": "2620.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they gave us a little bit of water at a time and a little bit of food at a time, so we don't get sick and die.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put us back on our feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they shipped us to a place called Muhldorf.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's in Bayern.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just, just myself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lost the others, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, not until after the war, when I met my brother on the way home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- they shipped us from, from Dachau to Muhldorf.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was in the forest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why they called it the Waldlager.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to even cut down trees and then put up these pre-fabricated barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, and then they used to send us out to work carrying cement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just put a sack of cement on the back and you carried it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what I heard from other people-- what they were building is an underground airfield.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] And that was in the summertime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For the winter, they, they built another camp a little further down, which was bunkers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was more like-- half of it was underground and the other half has a roof on top of it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember one time-- you know, you hear the air raids.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, they were bombing the railroads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one time, they hit the four corners of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I guess that was a mark that they knew it was a camp, a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But nobody got hurt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And one time, we went on the-- they bombed the railroad track.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The railroads-- you know, the cars, whatever they were shipping.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we used to go down there and clean that up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one car load of sugar-- that they were transporting sugar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we were eating sugar like crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
